“If you want to take interesting pictures, put interesting things in front of your camera.”

Caitie is a New Jersey based traveling model with over eight years of experience posing for body paintings, figure drawing classes, fine art, and glamour photographers. She has been published in magazines, printed in books, featured at gallery shows, strutted down runways, and captured in bronze.

 

Caitie is also a body painter, fosters cats, studies business, travels to foreign countries, and drinks black coffee. Her favorite color is chartreuse, and she really dislikes writing in the third person, although it seems like a professional thing to do.
♡
